#  Tailwind CSS Grid — Short Note

 `grid` = grid system on
 `grid-cols-12` = 12 column create
 `gap-4` = spacing

---

#  12 Column System

 পুরো row = 12 column

Example:

12 = full width
6 + 6 = 2 equal box
4 + 4 + 4 = 3 equal box
3 + 3 + 3 + 3 = 4 equal box

---

 `4 + 4 + 4 = 12`

 3 equal container

---

 mobile = 1 column
 medium screen = 3 column

---

